                        %mend rcSetDS; 
                        /*==========================================================================* 
                                     * Step:            AM_rrap_mor_bns_autoexec              A57SWEI7.BK0012QP * 
                                     * Transform:       AM_rrap_mor_bns_autoexec                                * 
                                     * Description:     BNS Mortgage jobs imported from IW503 leverage this     * 
